    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 power plant is in peak operational state, featuring a meticulously maintained high-pressure VANOS system and synchronized individual throttle bodies. This chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential, providing unparalleled mechanical grip. With zero bolster wear and an exhaustive service history, this specimen maintains its factory-spec torsional rigidity and throttle response. A turn-key acquisition for the purist seeking an uncompromised driving experience.",
